Subject: RE: [T2] Seat Stand/Pedestal  Mats

 Wolfsberg West are the people that make the mats. They only make the seat
pedastal pieces and not the fill in pieces. WW did have a run of 67 and
earlier mats that were made black instead of gray! Depending on where you
got them you might have gotten a set of the WW split bus mistake mats
instead of the correct 68 and later mat.

ronnie

